          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Bettering Resources in Guarding from Human Trafficking Act of 2016 or the BRIGHT Act of 2016</b></p> <p> This bill amends the federal criminal code to establish a five-year mandatory minimum prison term for certain offenses related to peonage, slavery, involuntary servitude, forced labor, and trafficking.</p>]]></text>
